Hallstatt唔多講，係靚嘅，不過遊客多，係好多好多，最多遊客係從側邊影Hallstatt，但其實係山腰影都靚。 你係Hallstatt抬高頭望過對面山頂，果度有個景點叫5fingers，<a href=\"https://dachstein-salzkammergut.com/en/summer/above-ground/5fingers/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdachstein-salzkammergut.com%2Fen%2Fsummer%2Fabove-ground%2F5fingers%2F&d=CDoAsJUKGFdMBzCvM33nWJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=1bef4bc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://dachstein-salzkammergut.com/en/summer/above-ground/5fingers/</a> 有吊車上山頂，山腳車站名叫 Dachstein，好天的話當行吓山，風景一流<br />\n<br />\n若果你揸車的話可以試埋呢條上條阿爾卑斯山嘅車路<a href=\"https://www.grossglockner.at/gg/en/index\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.grossglockner.at%2Fgg%2Fen%2Findex&d=CDoAsJUKGFdMBzCvM33nWJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=8302de15\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.grossglockner.at/gg/en/index</a>  上面九曲十三彎，但好多遊客上去睇阿爾卑斯山冰川，不過小心有高山症，因為最高點係海拔2400米以上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/052951_384f516f14df3eb50bbeecbcc3a368d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F052951_384f516f14df3eb50bbeecbcc3a368d6.jpg&h=6be61815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/052953_d8736bd8b1caa735a2e573377662c866.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F052953_d8736bd8b1caa735a2e573377662c866.jpg&h=b8ca09fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/052956_6f763d90f135225711ad9ec10dcc1efc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F052956_6f763d90f135225711ad9ec10dcc1efc.jpg&h=b1e0c995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/052958_3638aa54cabd73663b303c84b9c1b522.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F052958_3638aa54cabd73663b303c84b9c1b522.jpg&h=84e4c62b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/052959_90f3c9c15dfa58d41a006977f00dcb56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F052959_90f3c9c15dfa58d41a006977f00dcb56.jpg&h=b213a17d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1447853fcc53dc5cb9d264e2f194d8b72df85d4d","tid":569013,"uid":51744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T21:41:26.000Z","msg":"Bratislava 好特別嘅景點少，但都唔係無。<br />\n<br />\n呢個首都好多得意銅像，<a href=\"http://www.welcometobratislava.eu/statues-bratislava-old-town/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.welcometobratislava.eu%2Fstatues-bratislava-old-town%2F&d=CDoAsJUKGFdMBzCvM33nWJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=0247bad5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.welcometobratislava.eu/statues-bratislava-old-town/</a><br />\n<br />\n有間淺紫色嘅教堂 <a href=\"https://www.visitbratislava.com/places/blue-church/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.visitbratislava.com%2Fplaces%2Fblue-church%2F&d=CDoAsJUKGFdMBzCvM33nWJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=5e57141b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.visitbratislava.com/places/blue-church/</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有Bratislava Castle <a href=\"https://www.visitbratislava.com/places/bratislava-castle/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.visitbratislava.com%2Fplaces%2Fbratislava-castle%2F&d=CDoAsJUKGFdMBzCvM33nWJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=9e419f47\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.visitbratislava.com/places/bratislava-castle/</a><br />\n<br />\n我諗你交通連漫步，可以預一日"},{"pid":"f888df54a498a45da47bef0bdad0ded5f3245197","tid":569013,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6fc5c68605c960a0a65e8289cf2ed86cc40196e","tid":569013,"uid":51744,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7db25cd5371bc1911521be20bc6d7e7b6171c3dc","tid":569013,"uid":107567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T10:08:18.000Z","msg":"咁近, 咁樣就已去左兩個國家首都"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T21:30:14.000Z","msg":"你未去過都值得睇嘅<br />\n<br />\n維也納 Sch&ouml;nbrunn 後花園整得幾靚，又有迷宮，係山丘上面影返皇宮幾靚<br />\n<br />\n有時間去埋Kunsthistorisches Museum （Art history museum），我係藝術門外漢，但入面啲藝術品真係好好睇，你可以上網望吓先。<br />\n<br />\n我諗你預兩日都夠。<br />\n<br />\nHallstatt唔多講，係靚嘅，不過遊客多，係好多好多，最多遊客係從側邊影Hallstatt，但其實係山腰影都靚。 你係Hallstatt抬高頭望過對面山頂，果度有個景點叫5fingers，<a href=\"https://dachstein-salzkammergut.com/en/summer/above-ground/5fingers/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdachstein-salzkammergut.com%2Fen%2Fsummer%2Fabove-ground%2F5fingers%2F&d=CDoAsJUKGFdMBzCvM33nWJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=1bef4bc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://dachstein-salzkammergut.com/en/summer/above-ground/5fingers/</a> 有吊車上山頂，山腳車站名叫 Dachstein，好天的話當行吓山，風景一流<br />\n<br />\n若果你揸車的話可以試埋呢條上條阿爾卑斯山嘅車路<a href=\"https://www.grossglockner.at/gg/en/index\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.grossglockner.at%2Fgg%2Fen%2Findex&d=CDoAsJUKGFdMBzCvM33nWJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=8302de15\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.grossglockner.at/gg/en/index</a>  上面九曲十三彎，但好多遊客上去睇阿爾卑斯山冰川，不過小心有高山症，因為最高點係海拔2400米以上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/052951_384f516f14df3eb50bbeecbcc3a368d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F052951_384f516f14df3eb50bbeecbcc3a368d6.jpg&h=6be61815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/052953_d8736bd8b1caa735a2e573377662c866.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F052953_d8736bd8b1caa735a2e573377662c866.jpg&h=b8ca09fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/052956_6f763d90f135225711ad9ec10dcc1efc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F052956_6f763d90f135225711ad9ec10dcc1efc.jpg&h=b1e0c995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/052958_3638aa54cabd73663b303c84b9c1b522.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F052958_3638aa54cabd73663b303c84b9c1b522.jpg&h=84e4c62b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/052959_90f3c9c15dfa58d41a006977f00dcb56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F052959_90f3c9c15dfa58d41a006977f00dcb56.jpg&h=b213a17d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T08:46:20.000Z","msg":"早幾日喺Hallstatt，白雪一片好多人"}]}